## Heather’s Mission

As a third-generation Mt. Shasta native and founder of Heather Moyer Wellness (est. June 2020), Heather believes everyone has an inner warrior, even when wounded. After transforming her own life from rock bottom and navigating the loss of her son, she’s dedicated to helping you integrate grief, overcome limitations, and embrace hope. Using holistic tools like yoga, mindfulness, and nutrition, her retreats make mental, emotional, and physical well-being accessible to all.

